dit-Steve-Gullick-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Mary-In-The-Junkyard.-Credit-Steve-Gullick-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Mary-In-The-Junkyard.-Credit-Steve-Gullick-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Mary-In-The-Junkyard.-Credit-Steve-Gullick-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Mary-In-The-Junkyard.-Credit-Steve-Gullick-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Mary-in-the-Junkyard">Mary In the Junkyard</a>分享了他们的怀旧新单曲“This Is My California”——请在下面查看。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/mary-in-the-junkyard-this-old-house-ep-review-radar-3756137">《垃圾场里的玛丽》——《这座老房子》EP 评论：迷人的流行艺术超越了炒作</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌由 Craig Silvey（ <a href="/artists/sam-fender">Sam Fender</a> 、 <a href="/artists/wunderhorse">Wunderhorse</a> ）制作，由 Clari Freeman-Taylor、Saya Barbaglia 和 David Addsion 组成的乐队用 Freeman-Taylor 柔和的歌声和 Barbaglia 深沉的低音线条描绘了一幅他们自己的天堂的舒缓图画。</p><p>在新闻稿中谈到这首歌时，乐队分享道：“《这是我的加州》是一首关于寻找自己梦想的怀旧歌曲。通过电影和电视看到“加州”总是感觉像是一个天堂或成功的想法，但并没有真正引起我的共鸣。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="垃圾场里的玛丽 - 这是我的加利福尼亚（官方音频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9t60aQndiFo?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “歌曲中还有很多关于“Something lift you out”的歌词——在成长过程中，我和我的朋友们会攀爬一切，屋顶和树木，也许是为了感觉我们正在逃离我们所处的地方，或者感受到一种奇迹从高处看它有多么小。”</p><p>这首新歌是继今年早些时候发行的首张EP“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/mary-in-the-junkyard-this-old-house-ep-review-radar-3756137">This Old House</a> ”之后的。在对<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/mary-in-the-junkyard-this-old-house-ep-review-radar-3756137">这张 EP 的四星评论</a>中， <em>NME</em>分享道：“他们可能并不害怕在杂草中翻找，但《垃圾场里的玛丽》的梦想野心对于病毒式传播来说实在是太伟大了——让他们的音乐倾泻而出。您的扬声器并融入您的生活。走出去，体验这支乐队的血肉、勇气和勇气，感受他们的荣耀和承诺。”</p><p> Mary In The Junkyard 也将与<a href="/artists/Sports-Team">Sports Team</a>一起踏上英国巡演之路，并将前往纽约，在这座大城市进行两场演出，其中一晚为 Model/Actriz 提供支持，并在 Baby&#39;s All Right 举办他们的首场头条秀。他们还计划明年初在伦敦 Fabric 演出，这是他们迄今为止规模最大的现场表演。查看下面的完整旅游日期列表并访问<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fmary-in-the-junkyard-tickets%2Fartist%2F5433485" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>购买门票。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_6C-W5NJ3m/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.86